<p>New features added and be compatible with SVN r3627</p>

<p>New Features:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Custom notification mail with theme</li>
  <li>Be able to unsubscribe notification</li>
  <li>Author can get one level deeper than max depth for making the last reply</li>
</ul>

